The paper deals with the problem of landmark recognition using features extracted from CNNs, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the creation of R-MAC descriptors and a novel retrieval technique, which could also fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of fine-tuning strategies, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
